                    However, due to more direct flights from the U.S and Iceland, <a href="http://www.skyscanner.se/transport/flights/atl/osl/160714/160718/airfares-from-atlanta-hartsfield-jackson-to-oslo-gardermoen-in-july-2016.html?adults=1&children=0&infants=0&cabinclass=economy&rtn=1&preferdirects=false&outboundaltsenabled=false&inboundaltsenabled=false#results" target="_blank">oslo gardemoen (osl)</a> is also worth looking in to.<br />
